<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Javascript on 二次元の技术宅</title><link>/tags/javascript/</link><description>Recent content in Javascript on 二次元の技术宅</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2020 13:24:40 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/javascript/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>iView使用总结</title><link>/post/2020/02/iview/</link><pubDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2020 13:24:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/2020/02/iview/</guid><description/></item><item><title>将live2d猫咪整合到Hugo主题LoveIt</title><link>/post/2020/02/hugo-loveit-with-live2d-cats/</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2020 23:12:59 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/2020/02/hugo-loveit-with-live2d-cats/</guid><description>&lt;p>自建博客，一直想在页面上弄个“人格”，比如“伪春菜”。后来，朋友给我分享了&lt;a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/57a4deab12cc" target="_blank">领一只动态卡哇伊的小猫咪到你的网站吧 live2d入门&lt;/a>这篇文章。觉得挺合适，一白一黑两只猫模型，刚好LoveIt主题也是黑白。更何况，我还是个铲屎官。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>JS获取浏览器窗口的宽度高度</title><link>/post/2017/03/js-get-view-size/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Mar 2017 13:32:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/2017/03/js-get-view-size/</guid><description>&lt;p>有时候并不能简单的使用CSS来控制页面元素的大小，结合js来控制元素的大小会更方便一些，因此有时就需要用js获取浏览器窗口的尺寸。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>